\c 126 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 126\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Boo'ichi Gammachuutti Diddiiramuu Isaa (Weedduu ittiin ol ba'an)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yeroo Waaqayyo warra Xiyoonitti galan deebisee fide, nuyi akka warra abjuu abju'atanii taane.
\m \bd 2\bd* Yommus nuyi kolfa duwwaa taane, arrabni keenyas sagalee gammachuu guddisee dhageessise; saba lafa irraa keessatti immoo, "Waaqayyo waan guddaa isaaniif hojjetee argisiise" jedhamee in dubbatama.
\m \bd 3\bd* Waaqayyo waan guddaa nuuf hojjetee argisiiseera; nuyi warra gammachuu in taane.
\m \bd 4\bd* Akkuma biyya gara mirgaatii manii bishaanii isa goge deebiftee guuttu, yaa Waaqayyo, iddootti nu deebisi!
\m \bd 5\bd* Warri imimmaan dhangalaasaa sanyii facaasan, sagalee gammachuu dhageessisaa in haammatu.
\m \bd 6\bd* Inni sanyii facaafamuu baatee boo'aa adeemu, bissii isaa baadhatee, sagalee gammachuu dhageessisaa deebi'ee in gala.
\b 
